{"id": "1451061647207567372", "channel_id": "1449133326139916419", "type": 19, "author_id": "1006434911399465050", "author_name": "kalaidoskope", "author_bot": false, "content": "since you have castor e3 (great!) but pollux at e0, you might want to invest in pollux. i play the twins together (both at e3+) and pollux’s damage scaling w sacred heart + onyx plumes to keep drawing is absolutely insane.\n\ncorpo really likes her e2 if you wanna use her as a shielder. her rouse gives crazy shield on tentacle stance switch, + her ult is good shield and hand refresh if u need that. castor’s a better shielder than her tho.\n\nfor your prototype, celeste e3 is always great (death resist and heal is goated. if you want to play uvhash he’s pretty much best at e3 as well. for the rest i cant give any solid advice bc im also decently new, but hope it helps!", "timestamp": "2025-12-18T04:00:56.116000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-18T04:01:38.735000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["249224359183515660"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1449146330323882100", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1449133326139916419", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "By the Silver Key Advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
